&lt;h1&gt;Executive Coach at FirstMind&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you passionate about people, psychology and coaching?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Do you thrive in a fast-paced environment where you will be responsible for sales, employee and leadership development? Do you want to be part of an exceptional organisation with talented, motivated, driven and committed people where working with and developing people matters the most? Then maybe you should join our team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
