&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As an employee in FirstMind, you learn to master understanding behaviour, coach, mentor and guide companies to succeed. You must therefore be able to sell by and through understanding the potential and challenges of leaders, managers and employees. You must be passionate about helping others make better people decisions now and in the future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As an Executive Coach at FirstMind you will be a crucial part of the entire sales journey from start to end - from lead sourcing, nurturing and selling through 1:1 development conversations with people in large and small businesses. You will be analysing and understanding talent profiles, educating and ensuring that our clients succeed in understanding their employees, so that they achieve the best possible outcomes in their organisation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
