&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;FirstMind emerged to build the world&#39;s best tool, and it’s based on 43 cognitive studies and 9 behavioural studies from leading universities. These studies are made on 1.2 million people, to create the absolute best starting point for understanding people, their strengths, challenges, motivation, etc., to create strong cultures and high performing teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Today, FirstMind works with top Danish businesses, helping everything from the British police and the Danish military, to startups and more established companies to make better and stronger people&#39;s decisions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Our goal with FirstMind is for everyone in the world to work at what they do best.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
